   [1mList Options                  [22mâ”‚              â”‚                                          â”‚
       Some  options which store lists of option values can have action suffixes. For example, the [1m--display-tags [22moption
       takes a [1m,[22m-separated list of tags, but the option also allows you to append a single tag  with  [1m--display-tags-apâ€[0m
